{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/scala-palyframework-curd-1/","webpackCompilationHash":"a7e2b21b509852c48099","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Beace Blog","author":"Beace Lee"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2e0db305-f061-5a09-99d3-aa358ef10fb3","html":"<h2>需求</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>为了更好更快更有趣味地学习<code class=\"language-text\">scala</code>这门编程语言，结合<code class=\"language-text\">play framework</code>在实际开发场景中的运用，目标建立一个简单的用户列表的<code class=\"language-text\">RSAD</code>（read，search，add，delete）系统。特别记录此次学习过程。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/BeAce/scala-and-playframework-userlist\">代码托管</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!--more-->\n<h3>效果</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/5ee38df9cb5155b2d6f2bad5207b65482de1929a/687474703a2f2f696d616765732d6d616e616765722e6f73732d636e2d7368616e676861692e616c6979756e63732e636f6d2f7374617469632f757365726c6973742e706e67\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/BeAce/scala-and-playframework-userlist\">更多效果</a></p>\n<h2>前提</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>必须具有<code class=\"language-text\">java</code>开发环境</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">eclipse</code>或<code class=\"language-text\">intellij</code>IDE</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">mysql 5.6</code>版本</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>该项目所有操作均是在<code class=\"language-text\">MAC OSX</code>上操作，不同操作系统本质相同，操作会略有差异</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>包含以下知识点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>下载<code class=\"language-text\">Activator</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>配置环境变量</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>命令行中生成第一个<code class=\"language-text\">Play</code>项目</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>下载<code class=\"language-text\">Activator</code></h2>\n<p>可以通过，<code class=\"language-text\">playframework</code><a href=\"https://playframework.com/download\">官网下载离线环境</a>,点击<code class=\"language-text\">offline distribution</code>下载。</p>\n<h2>环境变量</h2>\n<p>在<code class=\"language-text\">$HOME/.profile</code>中写入<code class=\"language-text\">activator</code>路径,并写入权限</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export PATH=/path/to/activator-x.x.x/bin:$PATH</code></pre></div>\n<h2>生成第一个<code class=\"language-text\">Play</code>项目</h2>\n<p>通过命令，分别指定了项目名称，与项目模板。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ activator new my-first-app play-scala</code></pre></div>\n<p>在此我用的是<code class=\"language-text\">play</code>的<code class=\"language-text\">scala</code>模板，也可以使用<code class=\"language-text\">play-java</code>.当使用命令：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ activator new</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">play</code>会让你选择你想要的模板，模板列表如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/play-scala-userlist/play-scala-1.jpg\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>项目搭建完成后，可以通过命令，来运行项目：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ run</code></pre></div>\n<p>如果没有全局中的<code class=\"language-text\">activator</code>没有生效，或者没有权限，可以将<code class=\"language-text\">activator</code>中的<code class=\"language-text\">activator</code>复制到项目根目录下，通过命令来运行项目：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ ./actiator run</code></pre></div>\n<h2>运行结果</h2>\n<p>项目运行成功后，在浏览器中打开<a href=\"http://localhost:9000\">http://localhost:9000</a>。运行结果如下图。可以从浏览器中获取基本的版本信息以及相应的文档。\n<img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/play-scala-userlist/runresult.jpg\" alt=\"run\"></p>\n<p>如果想要修改端口，可以通过如下命令，让服务启动在自定义端口：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ ./activator run -Dhttp.port=9001</code></pre></div>\n<p>控制台日志显示</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/play-scala-userlist/run.jpg\" alt=\"result\"></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"快学Scala+Playframework之增删改查——项目搭建（一）","date":"October 25, 2016"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/scala-palyframework-curd-1/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/react-state/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"react中state变化导致的问题"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/scala-palyframework-curd-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"快学Scala+Playframework之增删改查——路由与静态页面（二）"}}}}}